                // ...
            }
```

I would not recommend to directly change the `login/index.php` code, though and using customscripts (https://docs.moodle.org/dev/customscripts) to replace the `index.php` entry point with a modified one could be equally harder to maintain when you upgrade your Moodle to later versions.

