Instead of adding all markers directly on the map, you can add the markers on a separate layer, add your markers to a [layerGroup][1] and add the layerGroup to the map.
You can remove the markers using clearLayers() method.

    var markers = L.layerGroup([marker1, marker2]).addTo(map);
    markers.clearLayers();

